snippet.title: Kain Cobra - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Is the year 20XX, the two most powerful protectors of the Planet Blue has been taken to a trial by the Intergalactic Federation meanwhile an Alien attack is devastating everything.

Kain Cobra, the son of Buxios the darkest force has the mission to save them, save the planet and maintain the new world order in balance.

#indiegame #shooter #actiongames
